  <item rdf:about="https://is.enes.org/archive-1/phase-2/documents/deliverables/is-enes2_d2-1_update-of-enes-governance-rules/view">
    <title>IS-ENES2_D2.1_Update of ENES governance rules</title>
    <link>https://is.enes.org/archive-1/phase-2/documents/deliverables/is-enes2_d2-1_update-of-enes-governance-rules/view</link>
    <description>In support to its infrastructure activities, ENES Board has created two task forces. These task forces advise ENES on all issues relevant to High Performance Computing and to data infrastructure, to support and exploit climate simulations in Europe. This document presents their terms of reference and membership as of March 2017.</description>
    
    
