  <item rdf:about="https://is.enes.org/archive-1/phase-2/events/nemo-sea-ice-working-group-designing-a-strategy-for-sea-ice-development-in-nemo">
    <title>IS-ENES2 NEMO sea ice working group: designing a strategy for sea ice development in NEMO</title>
    <link>https://is.enes.org/archive-1/phase-2/events/nemo-sea-ice-working-group-designing-a-strategy-for-sea-ice-development-in-nemo</link>
    <description>NEMO has, with great success, brought together the West European ocean model development community to produce one of the few leading ocean modelling tools in the world. Yet regarding sea ice, there has not been a common development strategy, leading to duplications and to a waste of manpower, at the expense of scientific activities. </description>
    
    
